{"tid":1725304,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣「撐香港，要自由」演唱會","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T19:53:42.000Z","uid":305458,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fa023ab0894735e69292cfa1c2f13dc51e7179e1","tid":1725304,"uid":305458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"From 立場FB:<br />\n<br />\n滅火器【特別分享】滅火器 Fire EX. Ｘ 林夕   MV「雙城記」<br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立樂團「滅火器」今日推出全新歌曲〈雙城記〉（City of Sadness，悲傷之城），歌曲由香港作詞人林夕填詞。MV全為香港抗爭的影片、照片，聲援香港抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n據滅火器貼文，主唱及作曲人楊大正表示，這首歌是在今年3月寫下，曲末引用了台灣電影《悲情城市》的經典配樂，原本想以1950、60年代的台灣作為背景，但恰好在6月時遇見林夕，「滅火器」遂有機會與這位香港傳奇詞人合作。<br />\n<br />\n滅火器表示，沒想到的是，香港現今的遭遇，卻與70年前受白色恐怖、黨國體制壓迫的台灣越來越像。<br />\n<br />\n滅火器在貼文寫上「光復香港 時代革命」，呼籲明晚到台北自由廣場參與「撐自由」演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ERZboYStq0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FERZboYStq0w&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=b113f4f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ERZboYStq0w</a><br />\n<br />\n聽晚就係喇！係youtube會有直播，得閒嘅手足可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30848a235a4305112a7e3d5275734a982610f99a","tid":1725304,"uid":305458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"p牌push唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完真係好有力量"},{"pid":"522675e2a7ecf1d46a2d1ab9a66cf7fc533f7be3","tid":1725304,"uid":305458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcdf0d3a917db1c44d7bbcc33ac6fdda86d123b","tid":1725304,"uid":165725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d91c346cac1b99836320a2b25a633b40a28909","tid":1725304,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"